title: Sokolska planina
text: Sokolska planina (<a href="Serbian%20Cyrillic">Serbian Cyrillic</a>: Соколска планина) is a <a href="mountains%20of%20Serbia">mountain</a> in western <a href="Serbia">Serbia</a>, near the town of <a href="Krupanj">Krupanj</a>. Its highest peak "Rožanj" has an elevation of 973 meters above sea level.
